node.text:
Our Lex Luthor action figure from DC New 52 is available for Pre-Order NOW at select retailers. Link in bio ⬆️⁠ ⁠
⁠
Lex Luthor uses his wealth and genius to not help humanity, but to destroy the Man of Steel! Luthor’s superior intellect is his deadliest weapon and he’s invented this high-tech, armored power suit to battle Superman! This 7" figure dons his green Power Suit and includes alternate hands, an art card and a base for posing. ⁠ ⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys⁠

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by McFarlane Toys on August 31, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, Superman and text that says 'LEX LUTHOR POWER SUIT JUSTICE LEAGUE: THE DARKSEID WAR PRE-ORDER NOW DC MULTIVERSE'.

node.text:
Our Lex Luthor with Throne action figure from Justice League: The Darkseid War is available for Pre-Order NOW at select retailers. Link in bio ⬆️⁠ ⁠
⁠
After the death of Darkseid in the Darkseid War, Lex Luthor absorbs the tyrannical ruler’s incredible power and leaves Metropolis for Apokolips. He creates a new blue power suit and becomes the new “God of Apokolips!” This 7" figure includes a throne accessory, an art card and a base for posing. ⁠ ⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #McFarlaneToys

node.text:

⁠
In the Dark Multiverse, Batman wields an evil Black Lantern power ring, which grants him the power to resurrect the dead. Now he leads an army of zombies across a twisted hellish landscape and wages war against the The Batman Who Laughs to save the DC Multiverse!⁠
⁠
#DCMultiverse #DarkKnightMetal #McFarlaneToys
